Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.64,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(192,521)\fs39\fscx98\pos(1170,1000.333)}Lekárske kancelárie (Po návštevných hodinách)\N Školská ošetrovňa
Dialogue: 3,0:01:56.72,0:01:57.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V školskej ošetrovni.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Školská ošetrovňa?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vy...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo ste ešte stále tu?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nenamáhaj sa.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som v poriadku, Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdalo sa, že to bolo dosť ťažké aj pre teba, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ty sa nazývaš vodcom?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne, vy...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tu robíte?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už by tu nemali byť žiadne Kage.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už nič nestojí v ceste.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, vieme.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak teda...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No ty si stále tu, nie?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si stále tu.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo by som na to mala povedať...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to len tip, ale...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že problémy, ktoré Yuri držali, miznú.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to pravda, Yuri?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... no, to je...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.  Použime moju hypnózu, aby sme to zisti{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choď odo mňa!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Súdiac podľa tej odpovede sa zdá, že sme to uhádli.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?  Počkaj, to vôbec nie je pravda.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som predsa len vodca.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak by moje problémy odišli tak ľahko...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola by som terčom posmechu.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak použime moju hypnózu, aby{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máte pravdu!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už sú všetky preč!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je na tom niečo zlé?!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, priznala to.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan, si zlá.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si len od prírody antagonistická, Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobrý návrat.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... to ma tak trocha robí šťastnou.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nazvala si ma Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To vyzerá, akoby sme boli kamarátky.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamarátky...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže sa zdá, že naše prípravy neboli zbytočné, hm?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prípravy?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo sa stane?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred koncom chceme niečo urobiť.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo, čo Kanade ešte nikdy nerobila.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde sú všetci ostatní?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci odišli.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rada to počujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretože si všetci navzájom pomáhali.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď nie bez pár problémov...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Pre Boha to bolo príliš ľahké.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale tak či tak...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci sa tu celkom bavili.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To som pochopil.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že to je aj vďaka tebe, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh áno, Takamatsu tiež odišiel.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď sa premenil na NPC, vrátil sa do normálu.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hé?  To je dobré.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevyzeráš moc prekvapene...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevravela si, že ľudia sa nemôžu vrátiť, keď sú z nich NPC?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.54,0:04:40.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že program bol vyrobený tak, že im sila citov môže vrátiť ľudskosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to za pieseň?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pohmkávala si si to, aj keď sme pracovali predtým.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čože to bolo...?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je tá pieseň.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá pieseň, ktorú Iwasawa-san spievala na konci.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Moja pieseň".
Dialogue: 3,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá pieseň...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá, ktorú ste vysielali po celej škole, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bóže.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to pekná pieseň, čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telocvičňa?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
