Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urobili sme to sami.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade spravila nápis.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan, nikdy si nepromovala?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslela som, že to môže byť zábava.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vôbec to nie je zábava.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzeralo to, že si sa bavila, keď si vypisovala listy.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dievčatá zvyčajne plačú.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Ženy sú vždy také.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, začneme?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?  Hneď teraz?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo myslíš, že si sa prezliekla?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, ja len...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premýšľala som, či naozaj zmizneme.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie som si istá, či už som pripravená.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ty sa nazývaš vodcom?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je s tebou?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vieš...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz, keď sú všetci preč, \Ntak si nejak stratila svoju vodcovskú auru.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V...Vážne?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, niečo sa rozhodne zmenilo.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?  Ako?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechaj ma popremýšľať...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, asi si viac dievčenská.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... mala by som byť za to rada?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alebo by som mala byť naštvaná?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.93,0:06:19.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz, keď už je po bitke, znova si nevinné a naivné dievčatko.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe má aj svoju rozkošnú stránku.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roz{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri je rozhodne zaujímavá.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, začnime!
