Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Úvodný prejav!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Začnime!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pre tých, ktorí bojovali v posmrtnom živote...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Začínajú promócie Bojiska posmrtného života!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz začneme spievaním Bojovej hymny!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bojová hymna?!  Čo je to?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pieseň Bojiska.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo ako náhrada za hymnu školy.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepamätám si, že by som písala niečo také.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Napísala to Kanade.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si to napísala?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No počkať, veď nie si ani v Bojisku!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, o to sa nestaraj.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, tu je text.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aká je melódia?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Školské hymny znejú všetky podobne, nie?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proste zaimprovizuj.  Budeš v pohode.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.16,0:07:11.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ideme na to!
