Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:40.52,Insert-English,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(0,1080)\an3}Ahhh, mabo tofu, mabo tofu.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je sakra s tou pesničkou?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekto to mal skontrolovať!  Práve som to zaspieval!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuž, Kanade-chan tvrdo a seriózne pracovala, aby to napísala.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Netreba sa rozčuľovať.  Však?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu je napísané tučným písmom "veselé číslo".
Dialogue: 3,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... ako to poviem?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že je to plné pocitov Kanade.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Od začiatku až po koniec.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zvládla si to, Kanade-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je ďalšie?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalšie je...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Udelenie promočných diplomov!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máme ich?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyrobili sme ich.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Znova hlavne Kanade.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, kde je riaditeľ, ktorý ich bude odovzdávať?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To budem ja!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:33.99,0:08:34.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh....
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne, prehral som v kameň-papier-nožnice!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš s tým problém?!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Tá rola ti sedí.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo vždy skončím s robením takýchto kravín?!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Začnime!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Udelenie promočných diplomov!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže teraz...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Kanade!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalší.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.04,0:09:24.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamura Yuri!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to na tebe dobre.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechaj ma na pokoji.
