Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idioti...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalší.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoi Ayato!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chvála mne.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bóže.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... ďakujeme za tvoje úsilie!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno!
