Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si príliš pomalý!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je jasné, že ty si bol príliš rýchly!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani náhodou, je tvoja vina, že si bol príliš pomalý!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sme spolu sedeli, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj {\i1}si{\i0} iný, keď si s Otonashim!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďme!
