Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:55.48,Insert-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,980)\an3}A tak je toto rozlúčka.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Záverečné slovo!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Týmto...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sa ukončila promočná ceremónia Bojiska posmrtného života!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolventi...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozchod!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Nechcem vidieť žiadnu ženu plakať...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odchádzam napred.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie si tu ty ten, čo plače?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby som ťa nikdy nestretol, Otonashi-san...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.03,0:14:47.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebol by som schopný ísť ďalej...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.12,0:14:54.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už nestratím svoju cestu.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veľmi ti ďakujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Môžeš ísť.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veľmi ti... ďakujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je preč?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak teda...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto je na rade s plačom?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja nebudem plakať.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, že som proti tebe vždy bojovala.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:28.65,0:15:32.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premýšľam, prečo sme neboli kamarátky skôr.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne ma to mrzí.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vieš, ako najstaršia dcéra
Dialogue: 3,0:15:39.16,0:15:43.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,som vždy musela starať o mojich hlučných súrodencov namiesto mojich rodičov.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naučila som sa od teba veľa, Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerala si tak nevedomo o svete,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tak som sa o teba naozaj bála.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohli sme urobiť... oveľa viac.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohli sme urobiť oveľa viac a zažiť oveľa viac zábavy.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.64,0:16:04.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby sme len mali viac času...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... toto už je zbohom, nie?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zbohom.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak ahoj.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj si mi veľmi pomohla.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobrá práca, vodkyňa.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre. Znova sa niekde stretneme.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ideme v poradí, tak som asi na rade.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem ísť prvý.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neodídeš a nenecháš tu Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja pôjdem.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja pôjdem.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem za všetko.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bez teba by nikdy nič nezačalo.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tiež by sme neskončili takto.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som za to vďačný.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlastne to bola náhoda.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keď sa nad tým zamyslíš, vôbec som tu nemal byť.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakoniec...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som našiel náplň svojho minulého života.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale stratil som tieto spomienky
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a skončil som tým, že som zablúdil do tohoto sveta.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretože som si na to spomenul...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:29.31,0:17:33.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,v tomto svete som sa dozvedel, čo je naplnený život.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže tak.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si bol vážne niekto špeciálny, že?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:41.03,0:17:45.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako som povedal, bola náhoda, že som všetkým pomohol.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nerozprávajme o tom naveky.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odchádzam.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:52.84,0:17:53.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak uvidíš Yui, pozdrav ju.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stále by mi malo ostať nejaké šťastie, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozhodne ho všetko využijem!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa, kamoš!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako sa ti páčila ceremónia?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola to zábava?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej. Veľká.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No koniec je tak trocha osamelý, čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, no je to ako začiatok cesty.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci sa tešia, ako začnú nový život.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je to dobre?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďme von.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nadýchať sa vzduchu...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.78,0:18:55.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Kanade...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chceš tu zostať?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len ma to tak napadlo...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Popremýšľaj o tom. Ako Yuri a Hinata...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vylúčení z krutého života...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budú aj ďalší, ktorí sem prídu, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.52,0:19:32.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne ako Yuri a ostatní, mohli by sem prísť
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a trpieť naveky.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Búriť sa proti ich minulým životom.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vieš...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ostaneme,
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,pre nováčikov, ako teraz,
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,môžeme im ukázať, aké úžasné je byť nažive.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžeme im pomôcť spromovať.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.87,0:19:55.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je možné, že som sem bol poslaný kvôli tomuto účelu.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zostaneš tu so mnou?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade, ak tu so mnou zostaneš,
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,aj keď je to v tomto svete,
Dialogue: 3,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nikdy nebudem osamelý.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno som to povedal už skôr, ale...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcem byť s tebou.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odteraz chcem s tebou zostať.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo, Kanade...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja ťa milujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja ťa milujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo... nič nevravíš?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechcem to povedať.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ti poviem moje pocity,
Dialogue: 3,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,zmiznem.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretože...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.51,0:20:52.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som sem prišla, aby som ti poďakovala.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som dievča, ktoré mohlo žiť vďaka tvojmu srdcu.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:04.49,0:21:09.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Srdce, ktoré mi bije v hrudi aj teraz, je tvoje.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mám len jednu výčitku.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:13.79,0:21:18.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikdy som nemohla poďakovať osobe, ktorá mi dala moju mladosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vždy som jej chcela poďakovať.
